<lb n="0388b10"/><byline type="Translator">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智
<lb n="0388b11"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0388b12"/><p type="dharani">曩謨婆<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">歸命世尊</note>怛&CB00770;<note place="inline">二合</note>路枳也<note place="inline">三世亦三界</note>
<lb n="0388b13"/>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底尾始瑟吒<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">最殊勝</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>也<note place="inline">大覺者</note>
<lb n="0388b14"/>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">同前</note>怛&CB00135;也他<note place="inline">引。所謂。亦即說</note>唵<note place="inline">亦云一切法本不生。
<lb n="0388b15"/>亦云三藏。亦云如來無見頂相也</note>尾戍馱也<note place="inline">淨除</note>尾戍馱也娑摩娑
<lb n="0388b16"/>摩三滿多<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00085;婆娑<note place="inline">普遍照曜</note>娑頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉拏<note place="inline">舒遍</note>&CB03442;
<lb n="0388b17"/>底&CB00344;訶曩<note place="inline">六趣稠林</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;尾舜<note place="inline">入</note>弟<note place="inline">自性清淨</note>阿
<lb n="0388b18"/>毘詵者&CB00418;&CB00805;<note place="inline">灌頂我</note>素&CB03442;多<note place="inline">善逝</note>&CB00085;囉&CB00085;者曩<note place="inline">引。殊勝言
<lb n="0388b19"/>教</note>阿蜜哩<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">去</note>毘灑罽<note place="inline">甘露灌頂。亦云不死句灌頂。露者法身解脫</note>
<lb n="0388b20"/>阿<note place="inline">引</note>訶囉阿訶囉<note place="inline">云唯願攝受。唯垂授攝受。亦云遍攘脫諸苦惱</note>阿欲散
<lb n="0388b21"/>馱<note place="inline">引</note>囉抳<note place="inline">任持受命</note>戍馱也戍馱也<note place="inline">清淨修修</note>&CB00344;&CB00344;曩尾戍
<lb n="0388b22"/>第<note place="inline">如虛空清淨</note>鄔瑟膩<note place="inline">二合</note>沙尾惹也尾舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">佛頂最清
<lb n="0388b23"/>淨</note>娑訶娑囉<note place="inline">二合</note>囉濕弭<note place="inline">二合<note n="0388002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＝千？</note><sic n="0388002" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="千">十</sic>光明</note>散祖&CB00135;帝<note place="inline">驚覺</note>
<lb n="0388b24"/>薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB03442;多地瑟吒<note place="inline">二合引</note>曩<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0388b25"/>多<note place="inline">一切如來神力所加持</note>摩訶母捺哩<note place="inline">二合。印契。若廣釋。身印語印心印。金剛印。如理
<lb n="0388b26"/>趣般若說</note>&CB00085;曰囉<note place="inline">二合</note>迦也僧訶多<note place="inline">上</note>曩尾舜第<note place="inline">金剛鉤鎖
<lb n="0388b27"/>身清淨</note>薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;囉拏播野訥&CB03442;底跛哩尾舜弟
<lb n="0388b28"/><note place="inline">一<note n="0388003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＋（障）？</note><sic n="0388003" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="切障">切</sic>清淨。一切障者。所謂業障報障煩惱障。皆得清淨也</note>&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>底&CB00135;靺多
<lb n="0388b29"/>也阿欲舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">壽命增長皆得清淨</note>三麼耶地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>帝
