<lb n="0388c03"/>吒沒地舜<note place="inline">入</note>第<note place="inline">顯現智慧清淨</note>惹也惹也<note place="inline">最勝最勝。真俗二諦</note>尾惹
<lb n="0388c04"/>也尾惹也<note place="inline"><note n="0388006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昧勝勝＝殊勝殊勝&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0388006" corr="殊勝殊勝" resp="【原】">昧勝勝</sic>悲智二門</note>娑麼<note place="inline">二合</note>囉娑麼<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">念<note n="0388007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">待＝持？</note><sic n="0388007" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="持">待</sic>
<lb n="0388c05"/>定慧<note n="0388008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＋（應）？</note><sic n="0388008" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="相應">相</sic></note>薩&CB00085;沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>多舜第<note place="inline">入而佛加持清淨</note>&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c06"/>曰&CB00942;<note place="inline">二合菩提心堅固如金剛也</note>&CB00085;曰囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB03442;陛<note place="inline">證金剛藏</note>&CB00085;曰覽
<lb n="0388c07"/><note place="inline">二合</note>婆&CB00085;<note place="inline">願成金剛</note>&CB00418;麼麼<note place="inline"><note n="0388009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝我？</note><sic n="0388009" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="我">或</sic>議或為他念誦稱彼名字</note>設哩嚂薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c08"/>薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>難<note place="inline">引</note>者迦也尾舜弟<note place="inline">一切有情身清<note n="0388010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">清＝淨？</note><sic n="0388010" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="淨">清</sic></note>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c09"/>&CB03442;底跛哩舜第<note place="inline">一切趣皆清淨</note>薩&CB00085;怛他&CB03442;多三麼濕
<lb n="0388c10"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>娑地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">一切如來安慰<note n="0388011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝令？</note><sic n="0388011" resp="Taisho" cert="?" corr="令">命</sic>得加持</note>沒&CB00833;<note place="inline">二合</note>沒
<lb n="0388c11"/>&CB00833;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00155;馱也<note place="inline">令悟能覺。令悟能覺</note>舜第<note place="inline">普遍清淨</note>薩&CB00085;怛他
<lb n="0388c12"/><note place="inline">引</note>&CB03442;多<note place="inline">引</note>地瑟<note place="inline">二合馱</note>曩地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">一切如來神力所加持</note>
<lb n="0388c13"/>摩訶母怛&CB03272;<note place="inline">二合大印。所謂大印由入毘盧遮那曼荼羅。受灌頂已後。灌頂師受得本尊瑜伽三
<lb n="0388c14"/>麼地。觀智一念淨心。瑜伽相應行者別尊心等同毘盧遮那及諸菩薩。能現入相成道。速證薩婆若智也</note></p><p type="inline">娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0388c15"/>訶者涅槃義。所謂四涅槃。一自性清淨涅槃。
<lb n="0388c16"/>二有餘依涅槃。三無餘依涅槃。四無住處涅
<lb n="0388c17"/>槃。如上所譯。唐梵敵對。顯句標釋</p>
